Femi Branch (a mụrụ na Mee 14, 1970) bụ onye na-eme ejije, onye nduzi na onye na-emepụta ihe na Naijiria.
A mụrụ Branch n'ọnwa Mee 14, afọ 1970

Nne na nna ya bụ ndị nkuzi na Sagamu, Nigeria. Ọ gara Satellite Town Primary School na Amuwo Odofin tupu ọ gaa Airforce Secondary School na Ikeja. O mechara gaa Mahadum Obafemi Awolowo ebe, ọ bụ ezie na a nabatara ya maka ọmụmụ okpukpe, o mechara nweta nzere bachelọ nke nka na Dramatic Arts.

Branch malitere ọrụ ya na Mahadum Obafemi Awolowo n'afọ 1991, n'otu afọ ahụ ọ pụtara na egwuregwu yoruba akpọrọ Eniyan O mechara pụta na ihe nkiri akpọrọ Orisun (nke pụtara: Origin) nke ndị ọrụ nke Mahadum Obafemi Awolowo mepụtara mana mpụta mbụ ya na telivishọn bụ n'afọ 2003 na azụmahịa telivishọn MTN Group akpọrọ "Dance with me". Ọ pụtara na ọrụ Oscar na ihe nkiri soap opera akpọrọ Domino Kemgbe ahụ, ọ pụtago na ihe karịrị otu narị ihe nkiri Naịjirịa, ole na ole n'ime ha ka ọ mepụtara ma duzie.
